{"tid":113735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】【揸車煲劇】邨巴司機睇TVB劇 廖小姐：佢開到好大聲","createTime":"2017-02-09T08:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T13:57:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7098074a8b615693203a9dffeeabda4a44dd8ee","tid":113735,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:23:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170209&amp;guid=56279702&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170209%26guid%3D56279702%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW97ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=02e6a71a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170209%26guid%3D56279702%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=60529efb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170209&amp;guid=56279702&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-02-09 10:40:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n司機將電話放在錶板上一邊開車一邊煲劇，廖小姐將過程拍下。<br />\n坐車發現司機邊揸邊煲劇，你會點做？乘客廖小姐昨晚8時(周三)，在灣仔駱克道登上邨巴NR719返屯門，當時車上乘客有約40人。惟開車前，司機就將手機放在錶板上，以免攜裝置固定好，隨即點播無綫黃金時段劇集《親親我好媽》，全程約45分鐘車程，一邊開車一邊煲劇。<br />\n<br />\n「佢開到好大聲，仲同另一位乘客傾偈，話呢套劇都幾好睇！」廖小姐正坐在司機位後面，她指前晚也是坐同一位司機的車，落車時發現對方手機開住播劇，已經覺得有問題，只是來不及拍攝下來。昨晚遇到同一人，他又邊開車邊煲劇。她表示，約45分鐘的車程中，司機幾乎全程煲劇。雖然開車過程尚算平穩，未出現任何驚險場面，但她擔心，若路面有突發事件，或其他駕駛者開車出問題，司機一下子反應不來，後果不堪設想。廖小姐坦言當時未有即場指正該司機，「因為佢講嘢粗魯啲，又有講粗口」膽怯的她不敢出言干涉。<br />\n<br />\nNR719線由南記巴士客運有限公司營運，為大利巴士集團旗下一條邨巴線，來往屯門寶怡花園至灣仔，去程19元，回程18元，由於路線穩定，落客點少，車程比其他交通工具短，故相當受屯門居民歡迎，主要客路為寶怡花園、良景邨、紅橋及屯門巿中心居民。分早夜班次，逢一至五早更7時至8時半，每10分鐘一班；夜更為6時至9時35分，約15分鐘<br />\n一班。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》今早聯絡到南記巴士客運，該公司一名姓葉的經理看過讀者拍攝的相片後指，該司機的行為相當危險，「我哋公司唔容許呢啲司機」。他將會展開調查，若確定為屬下司機，將會嚴厲處理。<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線：63836568"},{"pid":"efa964b275eb8cb6f6fc6dc998b077e32fc5caf9","tid":113735,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb73ffe70bee0885c3e3099f04a1e0e5edd2aeb","tid":113735,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"cut左條線去，等佢晚晚放工睇Roadshow啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7921ea18181562463a522e3ae7809801b606a5ff","tid":113735,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767836307aa47b0dfa1108e6543160f782811c0f","tid":113735,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cut左條線去，等佢晚晚放工睇Roadshow啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴士司機睇到Roadshow咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439e5883c2675cdda7aa540dc35bf486aa455a6c","tid":113735,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:35:09.000Z","msg":"共產黨：每日播幾分鐘國歌話你知佢存在<br />\nＴＶＢ：無時無刻無處不在"},{"pid":"be8c971a13b0a9c960dc999c2e6827c876e956be","tid":113735,"uid":3436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>cut左條線去，等佢晚晚放工睇Roadshow啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴士司機睇到Roadshow咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n閱讀理解